                  </hi>. I live in Thompson's buildings, Red-cross-street, Borough. My husband's name is John—we missed a cask on Saturday evening last—I think this is it—it was in the yard, full of water.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner</hi>. As I was coming from my work, I saw it he—I took it home, and was going to find the owner.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18360509-name-1483" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18360509-name-1483" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
